start.about.p.2=The account is created for your business but you can add individuals to the account, who can make changes to the property details, once they’re registered. If an individual leaves your company, you can remove them from the account and replace them with a new person.
start.heading.registration=Registration
start.registration.p.1=The registration process asks for the individual’s details, as well as the company details. We need proof of ID for the individual as well as proof of their relationship to the company. This ensures that all data is secure and only available to people who have the right to see it.
start.registration.p.2=To use this service, you’ll firstly need a Government Gateway account. If your business doesn’t have one (even if you have one as an individual), you’ll need to register.
