start.registration.youNeed.1=register your business for a Government Gateway account
start.registration.youNeed.2=use your Government Gateway ID to register with the VOA
start.registration.youNeed.3=provide proof of identity (your National insurance number, your passport number and date of birth)
start.registration.youNeed.4=provide proof of your relationship to the property (such as a rates or utility bill)
start.registration.youNeed.5=create a VOA account for your business
